Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ihatovo{a made-up place from multiple Miyazawa's works, it also has an intentionally russian toponymic suffix -ovo, usually applied to villages and small settlements according to https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A4%E3%83%BC%E3%83%8F%E3%83%88%E3%83%BC%E3%83%96 - generally accepted spelling is Ihatovo, but as per the rules of romanization, might as well be Ihatov, pick whichever you like}. Ihatovo. Terminus.{/End of line./This is the final station}
