Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your pastures fare well this year?{牧場 is both livestock and grazing land, but I think it's the latter with next line in mind}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.68,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thanks to continuous{/widespead} spraying{/sprinkling/sowing}, \Nthey did exceptionally well{/they burgeoned}.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get in, everyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much \Nfor doing this each year for us.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stress it{/It's nothing}.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please.
