Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.83,0:02:27.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(340,140)\fs15\c&H02261E&\3c&H99B7B5&\blur1}Woodcutter \Nand his wife {/Woodcutter family couple's/husband and wife's" tomb (can't see the last character, guess it's "tomb")/Mr. & Mrs. Woodcutter (obviously, woodcutter is not a given name)}{according to the book, the silk factory guy buried them because he didn't know the names when found bodies in the forest}
