Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your blessing{lit is just "thanks to you"}, \Nour pastures are doing great again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way here, \Nwe stopped by Mr. Redbeard{/Akahige; later, this character does not have a real beard, but only a moustache instead, so might as well go with "Redmoustach"}'s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He greeted us with his usual hearty laugh{maybe "wide grin"}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was cheerful{/smiling}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, everyone's laughter \Nreaches you too, right?
